<!-- About (about_), Practice reports / Recordings (rec_), Pitch Analyzer (debug_).
     The Pitch Analyzer is a beta diagnostics tool (stays on Home during beta, Sarah's call).
     Its raw diagnostic-row keys (raw/smoothed/accepted/noise/…) and the engine-config line stay
     English on purpose — they mirror the JSONL/log vocabulary a report is read against
     (plan §B.6). The chrome, buttons and status words around them are localized. -->
